  "texts": [
    "By dynamically directing queries to the most appropriate retrieval paths, agents ensure that each request is processed using the method best suited to its nature and context.",
    "This adaptability is essential for multi-source systems, where queries may require access to diverse data types, including unstructured text, structured databases, or even real-time APIs.",
    "In our framework, specialized agents such as Router Agents, RAG Agents, and SQL Agents work in tandem to manage these complexities and provide seamless query handling [Lewis et al., 2020].",
    "Router Agents act as the central decision-makers within the system.",
    "When a query is received, the Router Agent analyzes its structure and intent to determine the optimal processing strategy."
  ],
